                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-142-victim1278 t18320405-142-viclabel858"></join>, in the employ of the surveyor of the highways. On the 28th of February I lost a shovel, which I had left in Mr. Evans' premises - I saw it again as I was coming from chapel, and knew it to be mine; the prisoner knew where I kept my tools - he had worked with them.</p>


               <p>
            
