            , (Police-constable V 159.) I know where these tools were kept; I saw the prisoner in the yard, and apprehended him, as he came over the fence, about half-past five o'clock - he said he was going to work with the shovel; he ran from me - I took him again; he then said he stole the shovel, but was compelled to do it from want.</p>
